019	PSA	033	009	For he spake, and it was done; He commanded, and it stood fast.
019	PSA	033	010	The LORD bringeth the devices of the nations to nothing; He frustrateth the designs of kingdoms.
019	PSA	033	011	The purposes of the LORD stand for ever; The designs of his heart, to all generations.
019	PSA	033	012	Happy the nation whose God is Jehovah; The people whom he hath chosen for his inheritance.
019	PSA	033	013	The LORD looketh down from heaven; He beholdeth all the children of men;
