019	PSA	101	006	Mine eyes shall be upon the faithful of the land, that they may dwell with me; He that walketh in the way of uprightness shall serve me.
019	PSA	101	007	He who practiseth deceit shall not dwell in my house; He who telleth lies shall not remain in my sight.
