019	PSA	102	006	I am like the pelican of the wilderness; I am like an owl amid ruins.
019	PSA	102	007	I am sleepless; I am like a solitary bird upon the house-top.
019	PSA	102	008	All the day long my enemies reproach me; They who rage against me curse by me.
