019	PSA	102	018	This shall be written for the generation to come, That the people to be born may praise Jehovah.
019	PSA	102	019	For he looketh down from his holy height, From heaven doth he cast his eye upon the earth,
019	PSA	102	020	To listen to the sighs of the prisoner. To release those that are doomed to death;
019	PSA	102	021	That they may declare the name of Jehovah in Zion, And his praise in Jerusalem,
019	PSA	102	022	When the nations are assembled together, And the kingdoms to serve Jehovah.
019	PSA	102	023	He hath weakened my strength on the way, He hath shortened my days.
