019	PSA	103	019	The LORD hath established his throne in the heavens, And his kingdom ruleth over all.
019	PSA	103	020	Bless the LORD, ye his angels, Ye mighty ones who do his commands, Hearkening to the voice of his word!
019	PSA	103	021	Bless the LORD, all ye his hosts; Ye, his ministers, who do his pleasure!
019	PSA	103	022	Bless the LORD, all his works, In all places of his dominion! Bless the LORD, O my soul!
019	PSA	104	001	Bless the LORD, O my soul! O LORD, my God! thou art very great! Thou art clothed with glory and majesty!
