023	ISA	062	007	And give him no rest, Until he establish Jerusalem, and make her a praise in the earth!
023	ISA	062	008	Jehovah hath sworn by his right hand, and his mighty arm: No more will I give thy corn to be food for thine enemies, Nor shall the sons of the stranger drink thy wine, for which thou hast labored.
023	ISA	062	009	But they that reap the harvest shall eat it, And praise Jehovah; And they that gather the vintage shall drink it, In my holy comets.
